  'The ceiling team. Kazuha double-swirls Hydro and Pyro, buffing both Childe and Xiangling. Bennett + Kazuha + Xiangling core is one of the strongest in the game. High skill ceiling but the damage is unmatched.': ['The ceiling team. Kazuha double-swirls Hydro and Pyro, buffing both Childe and Xiangling. Bennett + Kazuha + Xiangling core is one of the strongest in the game. High skill ceiling but the damage is unmatched.', '天花板队伍。万叶双扩散水和火，同时提升公子和香菱的伤害。班尼特+万叶+香菱核心是游戏中最强的组合之一。操作要求高，但伤害无与伦比。'],
  'The classic Melt team.': ['The classic Melt team.', '经典融化队。钟离护盾保护甘雨安全蓄力。班尼特提升攻击力，香菱提供火元素附着。甘雨重击触发融化1.5倍伤害。甘雨最强单体输出配队。'],
  'The classic. High single-target + AoE. Consistent rotations. Easy to play. Perfect for Abyss.': ['The classic. High single-target + AoE. Consistent rotations. Easy to play. Perfect for Abyss.', '经典阵容。高单体+范围伤害。循环稳定。易上手。深渊完美选择。'],
  'The golden standard. XL + XQ + Bennett + Raiden. XL\'s burst snaphots Bennett\'s ATK buff. Devastating.': ['The golden standard. XL + XQ + Bennett + Raiden. XL\'s burst snaphots Bennett\'s ATK buff. Devastating.', '黄金标准配队。香菱+行秋+班尼特+雷电将军。香菱的元素爆发能锁定班尼特的攻击力加成，伤害惊人。'],
  'The quintessential Dendro team. Nahida marks enemies, Hydro creates cores, Electro triggers Hyperbloom. Kuki heals and triggers with full EM build. Extremely high floor damage with low investment.': ['The quintessential Dendro team. Nahida marks enemies, Hydro creates cores, Electro triggers Hyperbloom. Kuki heals and triggers with full EM build. Extremely high floor damage with low investment.', '典型的草元素队伍。纳西妲标记敌人，水元素创造种子，雷元素触发超绽放。久岐忍治疗并触发超绽放，全元素精通配置。低投入下伤害下限极高。'],
  'The timeless meta team. Bennett buffs Xiangling and Raiden simultaneously. Xiangling snapshots Bennett\'s ATK buff on her Pyronado. Raiden recharges the entire team. Consistent, high single-target and AoE damage.': ['The timeless meta team. Bennett buffs Xiangling and Raiden simultaneously. Xiangling snapshots Bennett\'s ATK buff on her Pyronado. Raiden recharges the entire team. Consistent, high single-target and AoE damage.', '经久不衰的版本答案队伍。班尼特同时为香菱和雷电将军增伤。香菱的旋火轮锁定班尼特的攻击力加成。雷电将军为全队充能。稳定的高额对单与范围伤害。'],
