  'XL + Chevreuse + Fischl + (flex). Overload meta with Pyro resonance. High ceiling.': ['XL + Chevreuse + Fischl + (flex). Overload meta with Pyro resonance. High ceiling.', '香菱+夏沃蕾+菲谢尔+（灵活位）。超载反应体系配合双火共鸣，上限极高。'],
