  'Xiao\'s best team.': ['Xiao\'s best team.', '魈的最强配队。珐露珊C6提供巨量风抗削减和风伤加成。芙宁娜通过气氛值放大所有伤害。闲云提升下落伤害并提供全队治疗。'],
  'Xiphos\' Moonlight': ['Xiphos\' Moonlight', '西福斯的月光'],
  'Yae/Fischl + Kazuha + Flex': ['Yae/Fischl + Kazuha + Flex', 'Yae/Fischl + 枫原万叶 + Flex'],
  'Yae/Fischl + Nahida + Flex': ['Yae/Fischl + Nahida + Flex', 'Yae/Fischl + 纳西妲 + Flex'],
  'Yelan': ['Yelan', '夜兰'],
  'Yelan + Kazuha + Bennett': ['Yelan + Kazuha + Bennett', '夜兰 + 枫原万叶 + 班尼特'],
  'Yelan + Nahida + Kuki/Raiden + Flex': ['Yelan + Nahida + Kuki/Raiden + Flex', '夜兰 + 纳西妲 + Kuki/Raiden + Flex'],
  'Yelan + Nahida + Kuki/Raiden + Flex. Yelan provides Hydro for bloom seeds. Kuki triggers hyperblooms. High floor damage.': ['Yelan + Nahida + Kuki/Raiden + Flex. Yelan provides Hydro for bloom seeds. Kuki triggers hyperblooms. High floor damage.', '夜兰+纳西妲+久岐忍/雷电将军+灵活位。夜兰提供水元素生成种子。久岐忍触发超绽放。基础伤害高。'],
  'Yelan + Xingqiu + Zhongli': ['Yelan + Xingqiu + Zhongli', '夜兰 + Xingqiu + 钟离'],
  'Yelan/Xingqiu + Kuki/Raiden + Flex': ['Yelan/Xingqiu + Kuki/Raiden + Flex', '夜兰/Xingqiu + Kuki/Raiden + Flex'],
  'Zhongli': ['Zhongli', '钟离'],
  'Zhongli + any 3 characters. His shield fits every team — hyperbloom, vape, freeze, Itto, Xiao. 20% universal RES shred benefits everyone.': ['Zhongli + any 3 characters. His shield fits every team — hyperbloom, vape, freeze, Itto, Xiao. 20% universal RES shred benefits everyone.', '钟离 + 任意三名角色。他的护盾适配所有队伍——超绽放、蒸发、冻结、一斗、魈。20%全属性减益对全队都有收益。'],
  '👥 Her highest ceiling team. Yelan and/or Xingqiu provide off-field Hydro for consistent Vaporize. Kazuha groups enemies and shreds Pyro RES with VV. Bennett buffs ATK — yes, Bennett is fine even though he heals; his ATK buff far outweighs the anti-synergy. Arlecchino\'s self-sustain from burst is enough.': ['👥 Her highest ceiling team. Yelan and/or Xingqiu provide off-field Hydro for consistent Vaporize. Kazuha groups enemies and shreds Pyro RES with VV. Bennett buffs ATK — yes, Bennett is fine even though he heals; his ATK buff far outweighs the anti-synergy. Arlecchino\'s self-sustain from burst is enough.', '👥 她的最高上限队伍。夜兰和/或行秋提供后台水元素以触发稳定蒸发。枫原万叶聚怪并用翠绿之影降低火元素抗性。班尼特提升攻击力——是的，即使他会治疗也无妨；他的攻击力加成远超过反协同。阿蕾奇诺通过元素爆发的自给自足已足够。'],
  '👥 No reactions, just raw Pyro dominance. Xiangling provides off-field damage and Pyro resonance (+25% ATK). Kazuha shreds RES and groups. Bennett buffs both Arlecchino and Xiangling. Consistent, easy to play, less dependent on EM substats.': ['👥 No reactions, just raw Pyro dominance. Xiangling provides off-field damage and Pyro resonance (+25% ATK). Kazuha shreds RES and groups. Bennett buffs both Arlecchino and Xiangling. Consistent, easy to play, less dependent on EM substats.', '👥 无反应，纯粹的火元素统治。香菱提供后台伤害和双火共鸣（+25%攻击力）。枫原万叶减抗并聚怪。班尼特同时提升阿蕾奇诺和香菱的攻击力。稳定易玩，对元素精通副词条依赖较低。'],
  '👥 Overload comp enabled by Chevreuse. Fischl provides off-field Electro for Overload triggers. Chevreuse shreds Pyro/Electro RES and provides ATK buff. Bennett rounds out the team. High single-target damage, excellent against bosses. NO HEALERS APART FROM BENNETT. Chevreuse\'s healing is minimal and optional — her buffs come from her passive, not healing.': ['👥 Overload comp enabled by Chevreuse. Fischl provides off-field Electro for Overload triggers. Chevreuse shreds Pyro/Electro RES and provides ATK buff. Bennett rounds out the team. High single-target damage, excellent against bosses. NO HEALERS APART FROM BENNETT. Chevreuse\'s healing is minimal and optional — her buffs come from her passive, not healing.', '👥 由夏沃蕾驱动的超载阵容。菲谢尔提供后台雷元素触发超载。夏沃蕾降低火/雷元素抗性并提供攻击力加成。班尼特补全队伍。对单伤害高，面对首领时表现出色。除班尼特外无需治疗。夏沃蕾的治疗量极少且非必需——她的增益来自被动技能，而非治疗。']
